After that, the drug couriers roam our country diligently.
The point is this: in Singapore it is prescribed that the laws are obliged to comply with ALL in a row, not just the humble and poor people.
It doesn’t matter who you are – a millionaire, a vice-premier, a famous artist or a resident of the European Union.
The option in this case is one: if you find half a kilo of cocaine, you will be hanged.
